    "Name": "Han Ya RR-S7H",
    "Details": "The RR-S7H is a Solaris VII gladiatorial design built by Firefly Foundry in 3105 using mixed Inner Sphere and Clan technology sourced from the Sea Foxes. An Apollo FCS-guided MRM 40 delivers the heaviest punch in the arena while a Large X-Pulse Laser provides powerful close-range backup despite its heat cost. Twin ER Medium Lasers and a Light AC/5 fill out a loadout designed to threaten opponents across every bracket simultaneously.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Well Balanced</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.08</color></b>",
